      <title>特斯拉交付量面临中国经济放缓和需求疲软的打击</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-deliveries-face-hit-china-slowdown-soft-demand-2024-03-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[预计特斯拉下周将报告第一季度交付量低迷，原因是其降价带来的提振作用减弱，而且这家美国汽车制造商在电动汽车市场放缓的情况下应对买家的激烈竞争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-deliveries-face-hit-china-slowdown-soft-demand-2024-03-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 09:37:25 GMT</pubDate>
